2
3
4
5
6
7
8
</pre></td><td class="rouge-code"><pre>.image-wrapper {
    text-align: center;

    .image-caption {
        color: $grey-color;
        margin-top: $spacing-unit / 3;
    }
}
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<p>And write in post like This
<!--  --></p>
